data.description: Must come see in person! Great opportunity for property to be income producing available! Proposal to lease for brine water with royalties has been received. Ask agent for more info! Tranquility on 30 acres with stocked pond. Enjoy sunrises while relaxing on the large front porch. Home has large eat in kitchen and plenty of space for entertaining. Freshly painted kitchen and living areas. Inspection report available. 2.5 hours from Dallas, 1.5 hours from Longview and 1 hour from Texarkana. The town of Naples is conveniently located 15 minutes away and has grocery store, winery and coffee shop. Assumable VA loan available.
